contentfulPagePressRelease.title: Qatar Foundation Celebrations at Darb El-Saai

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Image 1: Qatar Foundation’s Darb El-Saai tent visitors contribute to a piece of eco-friendly artwork by Qatar Green Building Council (QGBC).

Image 2: Children build robots by Texas A&M University at Qatar (TAMUQ) at Qatar Foundation’s Darb El-Saai tent.

Image 3: Qatar Biomedical Research Institute (QBRI) hosts DNA extraction workshop at Qatar Foundation’s Darb El-Saai tent.

Image 4: Children stand and pose in front of artwork at the entrance of Qatar Foundation’s tent at Darb El-Saai.

Image 5: Children construct houses and buildings using paper and Lego by Msheireb Properties at Qatar Foundation’s Darb El-Saai tent.

Image 6: Children put together a simple electric circuit by Texas A&M University at Qatar (TAMUQ) at Qatar Foundation’s Darb El-Saai tent.
